(11, 119, ' Perawatan Kursi', 'perawatan-kursi', '<div>Kursi yang digunakan setiap hari mudah mengalami kerusakan jika tidak dirawat:</div>\r\n<div>• Bersihkan kursi kayu dengan kain lembab dan keringkan segera.</div>\r\n<div>• Kursi berlapis kain bisa dibersihkan dengan vacuum atau sikat lembut.</div>\r\n<div>• Pastikan tidak goyah, kencangkan sambungan jika perlu.</div>\r\n<div>• Gunakan pelindung kaki kursi agar tidak merusak lantai.</div>\r\n<div> </div>\r\n<div>Kursi yang stabil dan bersih menunjang kenyamanan saat duduk.</div>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 2, '2025-06-26 08:23:58', 778, '', '2025-06-26 08:23:58', 778, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-26 08:23:58', NULL, '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":\"\",\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":\"\",\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":\"\",\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_image\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_article_format\":\"standard\",\"helix_ultimate_audio\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_gallery\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_video\":\"\"}', 1, 3, '', '', 1, 3, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
(12, 120, 'Perawatan Tempat tidur', 'perawatan-tempat-tidur', '<div> </div>\r\n<div> </div>\r\n<div>Tempat tidur yang terawat mendukung tidur yang nyenyak:</div>\r\n<div>• Putar kasur setiap 1-2 bulan untuk menjaga bentuknya.</div>\r\n<div>• Gunakan cover kasur agar terhindar dari noda dan keringat.</div>\r\n<div>• Bersihkan bawah tempat tidur dari debu dan kotoran.</div>\r\n<div>• Rangka kayu atau besi sebaiknya dilap dan diperiksa kekokohannya secara berkala.</div>\r\n<div> </div>\r\n<div>Tidur lebih nyaman dengan tempat tidur yang bersih dan sehat.</div>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 2, '2025-06-26 08:26:46', 778, '', '2025-06-26 08:26:46', 778, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-26 08:26:46', NULL, '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":\"\",\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":\"\",\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":\"\",\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_image\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_image_alt_txt\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_article_format\":\"standard\",\"helix_ultimate_audio\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_gallery\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_video\":\"\"}', 1, 2, '', '', 1, 5, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\"